CREATE TABLE "CrmRecord" ("id" TEXT NOT NULL,"type" TEXT NOT NULL,"name" TEXT NOT NULL,"description" TEXT,"status" TEXT,"data" JSONB NOT NULL DEFAULT '{}',"createdBy" TEXT NOT NULL,"createdAt" TIMESTAMP(3) NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,"updatedAt" TIMESTAMP(3) NOT NULL,CONSTRAINT "CrmRecord_pkey" PRIMARY KEY("id"));CREATE INDEX "CrmRecord_type_idx" ON "CrmRecord"("type");CREATE INDEX "CrmRecord_type_name_idx" ON "CrmRecord"("type","name");
